data.description: You will adore this unfurnished 3BR/2BA rental home in Destin. Located in Kel-Aire Gardens, this beautifully updated home features a mixture of flooring styles which includes hardwood, tile and carpet, an open floor plan and a bonus sunroom. The kitchen overlooks the living room and has been outfitted with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom is large and offers a spacious walk-in closet to accommodate storage needs. Outside you will find a beautiful, crystal blue pool and plenty of yard space for pets to play. Pool and Lawn Service is included in the rent and an "as is" washer/dryer have been installed for additional convenience. This home also features additional parking adequate for a boat. Available May 2 for a 12 month lease. Pet-friendly pending owner approval and deposit
